41
00:01:53,130 --> 00:01:54,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Alright.</font>

42
00:01:54,260 --> 00:01:57,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Let's hear this reason, then.</font>

43
00:01:57,390 --> 00:01:58,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'll pass.</font>

44
00:01:58,140 --> 00:01:59,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">H-Hey!</font>

45
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:01,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I don't care about her past.</font>

46
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Where are you going, Luffy?</font>

47
00:02:02,850 --> 00:02:03,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">For a walk.</font>

48
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:07,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">A-A walk?! You're not
gonna listen to this?!</font>

49
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nah. Pass.</font>

50
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:10,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What's with him?</font>

51
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:14,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Don't mind him.
That's just how he is.</font>

52
00:02:14,610 --> 00:02:16,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We'll hear you out.</font>

53
00:02:16,570 --> 00:02:19,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Though I doubt it'll make
much of a difference.</font>

54
00:02:19,950 --> 00:02:22,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah! I'll listen, too!</font>

55
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:25,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I wanna know what's
happening on this island!</font>

56
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:28,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Me, too! I want to know
everything about Nami!</font>

57
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">He's out like a light.</font>

58
00:02:32,130 --> 00:02:34,010
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Don't sleep right after saying that!</font>

59
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I see.</font>

60
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:42,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">So this is why Nami
is having such a hard time.</font>

61
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:48,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I fell asleep...?</font>

62
00:02:49,650 --> 00:02:50,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Huh?</font>

63
00:02:50,780 --> 00:02:51,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nojiko?</font>

64
00:02:53,570 --> 00:02:55,700
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Where could she have gone?</font>

65
00:03:01,490 --> 00:03:04,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Just a little more, Bell-mère.</font>

66
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:09,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Just a little more,
and we'll have it all back.</font>

67
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:12,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cocoyashi Village,
the tangerine orchard,</font>

68
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:13,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">and even my dream!</font>

69
00:03:20,890 --> 00:03:24,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It took eight years...</font>

70
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:37,320
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#000000">Nami (8 Years Ago)</font></font></b></font>

