72
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's done...</font>

73
00:03:35,650 --> 00:03:37,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's done!</font>

74
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:47,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Now I just need to check that book...</font>

75
00:03:57,470 --> 00:03:58,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh!</font>

76
00:03:58,590 --> 00:03:59,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami!</font>

77
00:03:59,930 --> 00:04:01,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What's wrong?</font>

78
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:04,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nothing!</font>

79
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nothing at all!</font>

80
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:17,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh, my!</font>

81
00:04:17,530 --> 00:04:19,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Damn it, Nami!</font>

82
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:21,700
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Not again!</font>

83
00:04:22,030 --> 00:04:23,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh? You did it again, Nami?</font>

84
00:04:22,450 --> 00:04:23,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82" color="#d6d6d6">Let go!</font>

85
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You just never learn!</font>

86
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm not a cat!</font>

87
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:29,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You idiot!</font>

88
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:32,460
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#000000">Genzo (8 Years Ago)</font></font></b></font>

89
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:32,460
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#fbfafa">Genzo (8 Years Ago)</font></font></b></font>

90
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:32,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">How many times do I have
to tell you not to steal?!</font>

91
00:04:32,710 --> 00:04:35,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's not our fault we're poor!</font>

92
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:38,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cheapskate!</font>

93
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:40,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère!</font>

94
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:42,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère!</font>

95
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:45,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Your no-good cat's been at it again!</font>

96
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:50,900
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#000000">Bell-mère
Nami and Nojiko's
Foster Mother</font></font></b></font>

97
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:50,900
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#faf9fa">Bell-mère
Nami and Nojiko's
Foster Mother</font></font></b></font>

98
00:04:48,810 --> 00:04:50,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What is it? Pipe down!</font>

99
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh!</font>

100
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Welcome home, Nami!</font>

101
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:55,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm back!</font>

102
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Look! This is the umpteenth time!</font>

103
00:04:57,900 --> 00:04:59,700
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She's infamous in the village now!</font>

104
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:02,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh? Is that so?</font>

105
00:05:02,780 --> 00:05:06,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Surely even you've stolen
something before, Mr. Gen?</font>

106
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>You're</i> the reason she acts like this!</font>

107
00:05:08,250 --> 00:05:09,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm just kidding!</font>

108
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Look, I get it.</font>

109
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:13,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You covered the cost, right?</font>

110
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:15,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">B-Bell-mère...</font>

111
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:16,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I can't thank you enough.</font>

112
00:05:16,710 --> 00:05:18,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Money's a bit tight right now.</font>

113
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:20,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'll pay you back later...</font>

114
00:05:20,590 --> 00:05:22,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">with my body.</font>

115
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:27,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I d-didn't mean it l-like that!</font>

116
00:05:28,850 --> 00:05:30,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You're beet red!</font>

117
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:38,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh? And why are <i>you</i> laughing?</font>

118
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:42,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm sorry!</font>

119
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:46,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But I really wanted this book!</font>

120
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:49,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">If you wanted it,
why didn't you just tell me?</font>

121
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:53,080
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You wouldn't have
bought it for me anyway...</font>

122
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Of course I would have!</font>

123
00:05:54,580 --> 00:05:56,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We've got some money stashed away.</font>

124
00:05:56,710 --> 00:06:00,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But the villagers said that
the weather's been so good lately,</font>

125
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:03,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">any old field will grow
tons of tangerines.</font>

126
00:06:03,550 --> 00:06:06,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We can't get a good price for ours,
and they won't sell anyway.</font>

127
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">They can mind their own business!</font>

128
00:06:08,850 --> 00:06:11,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You're so dumb, Nami!</font>

129
00:06:08,890 --> 00:06:11,270
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#000000">Nojiko (8 Years Ago)</font></font></b></font>

130
00:06:08,890 --> 00:06:11,270
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#fbfafa">Nojiko (8 Years Ago)</font></font></b></font>

131
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:14,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I would've stolen it way better!</font>

132
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:17,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I said no stealing!</font>

133
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:20,360
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I was just joking!</font>

134
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That hurts!</font>

135
00:06:26,530 --> 00:06:28,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But you know, one thing's for sure!</font>

136
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:32,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You really draw some
amazing maps, Nami!</font>

137
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:36,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You already learned how to draw
sea charts, and now land maps!</font>

138
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:40,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">This is a map of this island, isn't it?!</font>

139
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:45,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">No one would ever think
someone your age drew this!</font>

140
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:50,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I've been studying navigation, too!</font>

141
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Even navigation?!</font>

142
00:06:52,850 --> 00:06:54,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That's Nami's dream, after all!</font>

143
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:56,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah!</font>

144
00:06:56,270 --> 00:07:00,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm gonna use my navigation skills
to sail all the world's seas!</font>

145
00:07:00,940 --> 00:07:04,360
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">And then I'm gonna make
a map of everything I see!</font>

146
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:10,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That means this map of the island
is the first step towards your dream!</font>

147
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah!</font>

148
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">A map of the world, huh?</font>

149
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:19,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami! Someday, your
dream <i>will</i> come true!</font>

150
00:07:22,590 --> 00:07:24,010
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I just know it!</font>

151
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:30,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hey, Bell-mère.</font>

152
00:07:31,810 --> 00:07:33,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You haven't been eating lately.</font>

153
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:36,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm eating tangerines, aren't I?</font>

154
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm on a diet right now!</font>

155
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I don't need any food, either.</font>

156
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:42,440
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Since when are you
watching your figure?</font>

157
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:44,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Kids need to eat right!</font>

158
00:07:44,570 --> 00:07:46,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Stop lying!</font>

159
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:50,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You aren't eating because we
don't have any money, right?</font>

160
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:50,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Really?!</font>

161
00:07:50,990 --> 00:07:54,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You're suffering so that we can–</font>

162
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:54,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82" color="#d6d6d6">I'm on a <i>diet!</i></font>

163
00:07:54,370 --> 00:07:58,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You shouldn't underestimate
the rejuvenating power of tangerines!</font>

164
00:07:58,250 --> 00:08:03,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">They're the reason I still have such
glowing skin at the age of thirty!</font>

165
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:05,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But your hands are yellow.</font>

166
00:08:05,670 --> 00:08:07,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Just shut up and eat!</font>

167
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:11,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Here you go, Nami! It's done!</font>

168
00:08:11,140 --> 00:08:13,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's Bell-mère's own
<i>haute couture</i> brand!</font>

169
00:08:13,850 --> 00:08:15,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Another hand-me-down from Nojiko?</font>

170
00:08:15,890 --> 00:08:17,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Now, now!</font>

171
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:19,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It looks great on you, Nami!</font>

172
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:21,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">This lion used to be a sunflower!</font>

173
00:08:21,610 --> 00:08:23,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That's just how it goes!</font>

174
00:08:23,610 --> 00:08:26,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You're two years younger than I am!</font>

175
00:08:26,570 --> 00:08:28,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Age has nothing to do with it!</font>

176
00:08:28,610 --> 00:08:30,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I want new clothes, too!</font>

177
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:32,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Mine are old clothes, too, you know!</font>

178
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:36,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You get my stuff 'cause
you're my baby sister!</font>

179
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:39,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But I'm not even your real sister!</font>

180
00:08:39,330 --> 00:08:41,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We're not related by blood!</font>

181
00:08:42,380 --> 00:08:43,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami!</font>

182
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:52,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère!</font>

183
00:08:58,850 --> 00:09:01,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">So what if you're not
blood-related?!</font>

184
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:08,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Don't say something
that stupid ever again!</font>

185
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:10,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Wh-Whatever...</font>

186
00:09:10,530 --> 00:09:15,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's not like you're our
real mom, anyway!</font>

187
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:18,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You'd be better off
without us, wouldn't you?!</font>

188
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:21,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That way, you'd have enough to eat!</font>

189
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:25,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You could buy all the clothes
you want! You could be free!</font>

190
00:09:25,130 --> 00:09:26,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I wish...</font>

191
00:09:27,170 --> 00:09:31,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I wish someone richer
had adopted me instead!</font>

192
00:09:39,020 --> 00:09:39,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Is...</font>

193
00:09:39,930 --> 00:09:40,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">that so?</font>

194
00:09:42,060 --> 00:09:44,110
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Fine, then! Do what you want!</font>

195
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:47,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">If you hate this house so much,
feel free to go live somewhere else!</font>

196
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:49,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Stop it, you two!</font>

197
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:52,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Fine! I'm leaving!</font>

198
00:09:53,610 --> 00:09:54,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami!</font>

199
00:09:54,950 --> 00:09:56,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami!</font>

200
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:06,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère...</font>

201
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:09,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">The three of us are a family!</font>

202
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:11,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I bet Nami feels the same way!</font>

203
00:10:11,590 --> 00:10:14,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She didn't mean what she said!</font>

204
00:10:15,850 --> 00:10:17,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You're a good girl, Nojiko.</font>

205
00:10:18,180 --> 00:10:20,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That was real immature of me.</font>

206
00:10:21,430 --> 00:10:23,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Could you go bring
Nami back for me?</font>

207
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:26,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'll have a super awesome dinner
ready before you get back!</font>

208
00:10:27,570 --> 00:10:28,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Okay!</font>

209
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:41,540
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#000000">Cocoyashi Village</font></font></b></font>

210
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:41,540
<font face="Chinacat" size="99"><b><font face="DFPGiHi-W7-Strp"><font color="#fbfafa">Cocoyashi Village</font></font></b></font>

211
00:10:42,330 --> 00:10:44,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Alright, ma'am! How about this much?</font>

212
00:10:44,460 --> 00:10:47,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What? Can't you do better than that?</font>

213
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:50,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Right over here!
Come see our low prices!</font>

214
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:55,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You can't beat my fruit
when it comes to freshness!</font>

215
00:11:03,890 --> 00:11:07,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">So, coming here from the edge
of the village is "running away"?</font>

216
00:11:07,020 --> 00:11:08,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Must be pretty convenient!</font>

217
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:12,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Here. Drink up before it gets cold!</font>

218
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:18,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère would be
happier if we were gone.</font>

219
00:11:19,620 --> 00:11:20,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Why do you think that?</font>

220
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:24,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Having two kids costs a lot of money,</font>

221
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:29,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">and everyone in the village
hates her because of me.</font>

222
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:32,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You're old enough to
think about others now, huh?</font>

223
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:35,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Don't worry.</font>

224
00:11:35,050 --> 00:11:38,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She was a pretty infamous brat
when she was your age, too.</font>

225
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:40,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Really? Bell-mère?</font>

226
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:44,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She's <i>still</i> quite an infamous
brat in the villagers' eyes!</font>

227
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:48,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Imagine how surprised we were
when she suddenly declared,</font>

228
00:11:48,770 --> 00:11:50,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">"I'm going to be a Marine!"</font>

229
00:11:50,650 --> 00:11:51,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">A Marine?!</font>

230
00:11:51,980 --> 00:11:54,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère was a Marine?!</font>

231
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah...</font>

232
00:12:03,950 --> 00:12:08,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">"Pirates have to pay for
slaughtering innocent people!"</font>

233
00:12:08,460 --> 00:12:10,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">With those words, she left the village.</font>

234
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:22,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Just as she thought her
time had finally come...</font>

235
00:12:23,850 --> 00:12:26,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Well... I guess this is it...</i></font>

236
00:12:45,490 --> 00:12:47,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Is that your baby sister?</i></font>

237
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:54,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Nuh-uh. I dunno who she is.</i></font>

238
00:13:04,140 --> 00:13:06,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>She has no idea what's going on...</i></font>

239
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami, that girl...</font>

240
00:13:22,780 --> 00:13:24,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">was you.</font>

241
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:30,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">When she saw you, Bell-mère
mustered up the will to live again.</font>

242
00:13:40,380 --> 00:13:42,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>It </i>is<i> a boat! I knew it!</i></font>

243
00:13:42,590 --> 00:13:45,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>On a stormy night like tonight?!
Who the hell could it be?!</i></font>

244
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:55,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Doctor!</i></font>

245
00:13:55,980 --> 00:13:57,400
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Get the doctor!</i></font>

246
00:13:58,030 --> 00:14:00,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Bell-mère? Is that you, Bell-mère?!</i></font>

247
00:14:00,650 --> 00:14:01,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Bell-mère!</i></font>

248
00:14:01,490 --> 00:14:03,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>What in the world happened?!</i></font>

249
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:07,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Who are these–</i></font>

250
00:14:07,530 --> 00:14:09,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Doctor! They have terrible fevers!</i></font>

251
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:12,080
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>They're exhausted from the storm!</i></font>

252
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>What?!</i></font>

253
00:14:15,130 --> 00:14:16,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>R-Right, got it!</i></font>

254
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:19,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>But we need to tend to those
nasty wounds of yours, too!</i></font>

255
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:21,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Forget about that! Just hurry!</i></font>

256
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:23,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Please! Don't let them die!</i></font>

257
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i><font color="#eff4f3">Save them!</font></i></font>

258
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:30,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i><font color="#eff4f3">I beg of you!</font></i></font>

259
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:35,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>A delinquent like you...
What did you just say?!</i></font>

260
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:40,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I said that I'm going
to be their mother.</i></font>

261
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:41,400
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>You can't!</i></font>

262
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Don't do it!</i></font>

263
00:14:42,900 --> 00:14:45,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>A punk like you can't
possibly raise children!</i></font>

264
00:14:45,610 --> 00:14:49,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>L-Listen to me! Give them
to a government institution!</i></font>

265
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:51,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I've already made up my mind!</i></font>

266
00:14:52,410 --> 00:14:54,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I'm an adult now, too.</i></font>

267
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:56,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I was even a Marine.</i></font>

268
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I've tried to become more
of a decent human being.</i></font>

269
00:14:58,670 --> 00:15:01,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I'm going to be responsible
for raising these kids.</i></font>

270
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:04,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I'll raise them to be good people.</i></font>

271
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:06,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>The kind who won't be
corrupted by the world.</i></font>

272
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:10,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I'm going to live on with these girls.</i></font>

273
00:15:10,470 --> 00:15:13,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Nami and Nojiko saved my life.</i></font>

274
00:15:18,730 --> 00:15:23,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">The bond you three have
runs far deeper than blood.</font>

275
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:29,910
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami! I <i>thought</i> you'd be here!</font>

276
00:15:29,910 --> 00:15:31,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">N-Nojiko!</font>

277
00:15:32,040 --> 00:15:34,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère is waiting for us!</font>

278
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:36,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She's making a yummy dinner!</font>

279
00:15:38,630 --> 00:15:39,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Okay!</font>

280
00:15:40,290 --> 00:15:42,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I bet it's your favorite!</font>

281
00:15:42,090 --> 00:15:43,840
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Omelets with tangerine sauce!</font>

282
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:45,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yahoo!</font>

283
00:15:47,050 --> 00:15:51,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">– Yay! Omelets!
– Yay! Omelets!</font>

284
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pirates, everyone!</font>

285
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:00,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pirates are coming!</font>

286
00:16:01,690 --> 00:16:02,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pirates!</font>

287
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:05,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Everyone hide!</font>

288
00:16:14,700 --> 00:16:16,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's the Arlong Pirates!</font>

289
00:16:16,250 --> 00:16:17,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Arlong?!</font>

290
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:17,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That can't be!</font>

291
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:21,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Wh-What are fishmen from
the Grand Line doing here?!</font>

292
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:24,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Was the rumor about a split
in the Fishman Pirates true?</font>

293
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:26,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami! Nojiko!</font>

294
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:27,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Mr. Gen!</font>

295
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:29,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's dangerous here!</font>

296
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:31,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Go and hide in the woods!</font>

297
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:32,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Huh? But...</font>

298
00:16:32,970 --> 00:16:34,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Go! Now!</font>

299
00:16:45,730 --> 00:16:49,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You seem to be in high spirits
for a bunch of pathetic humans!</font>

300
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:54,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">As of this moment, this village– No, this entire island is under my control!</font>

301
00:16:56,620 --> 00:16:58,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Listen up!</font>

302
00:16:58,290 --> 00:17:02,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">On this glorious day, you will
all buy your lives from me!</font>

303
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You'll pay 100,000 per adult.</font>

304
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:09,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Each child is 50,000.</font>

305
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:11,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Those who can't pay will die!</font>

306
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:16,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What do we do, Nojiko?</font>

307
00:17:16,850 --> 00:17:19,100
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We can't pay that much!</font>

308
00:17:19,100 --> 00:17:21,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But they might not spot our house!</font>

309
00:17:21,600 --> 00:17:23,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You can't see it from the village!</font>

310
00:17:28,360 --> 00:17:30,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">How much did we get, brother?</font>

311
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:33,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Just over 25 million, I'd say.</font>

312
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:35,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Excellent!</font>

313
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:45,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sounds like we have to pay 100,000 berries
every month for the rest of our lives!</font>

314
00:17:45,090 --> 00:17:47,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pay 100,000...?! We can't
 even survive like that!</font>

315
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:48,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Endure it for now!</font>

316
00:17:48,710 --> 00:17:52,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We should just be grateful
no one in the village was killed.</font>

317
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:56,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">If it's only money they want,
that's an easy price to pay.</font>

318
00:17:56,720 --> 00:18:02,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I just hope they leave without
seeing Bell-mère's house.</font>

319
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:06,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">With the two children, it would
come to 200,000 berries...</font>

320
00:18:06,230 --> 00:18:08,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I doubt she has that much saved up.</font>

321
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:13,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Alright! Time to go, brothers!</font>

322
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:19,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Captain Arlong! There's smoke
coming from over there!</font>

323
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Okay!</font>

324
00:18:27,290 --> 00:18:28,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Alright, let's see!</font>

325
00:18:29,170 --> 00:18:33,010
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That's too good! Nothing's quite like
Bell-mère's special tangerine sauce!</font>

326
00:18:33,010 --> 00:18:35,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami and Nojiko are gonna
leap out of their seats!</font>

327
00:18:35,970 --> 00:18:38,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">The smoke is coming from a house!</font>

328
00:18:39,850 --> 00:18:41,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh?</font>

329
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:42,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We almost missed it.</font>

330
00:18:42,810 --> 00:18:44,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Damn!</font>

331
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:46,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">– Bell-mère!
– Bell-mère!</font>

332
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:49,110
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Come on! Let's go collect our money!</font>

333
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:53,360
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh no, this is bad! The pirates...</font>

334
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:55,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">...are headed to Bell-mère's house!</font>

335
00:18:59,450 --> 00:19:01,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hey! Nojiko and Nami are gone!</font>

336
00:19:01,870 --> 00:19:02,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What?!</font>

337
00:19:03,290 --> 00:19:05,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ten more minutes
for the duck in the oven.</font>

338
00:19:05,670 --> 00:19:07,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">The stew is boiling.</font>

339
00:19:07,290 --> 00:19:09,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">This'll really mess up our budget,</font>

340
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:12,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">but sometimes you've gotta splurge!</font>

341
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:22,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère's gonna...
Bell-mère's gonna...</font>

342
00:19:24,430 --> 00:19:26,440
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère's gonna be killed!</font>

343
00:19:33,990 --> 00:19:37,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We can't just abandon Bell-mère!</font>

344
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:39,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Damn! Why did this have to happen?!</font>

345
00:19:39,620 --> 00:19:41,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Don't jump the gun, Bell-mère!</font>

346
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:46,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh, are they back?</font>

347
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:55,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's open!</font>

348
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:57,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Come on in!</font>

349
00:19:57,590 --> 00:19:58,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pardon me...</font>

350
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:24,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You've got bad luck.</font>

351
00:20:24,330 --> 00:20:26,080
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm a former Marine.</font>

352
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:32,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What are pirates from the Grand Line doing out here in Cocoyashi Village?</font>

353
00:20:37,130 --> 00:20:38,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What's so funny?!</font>

354
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:49,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Weak! Weak! You're weak!
So weak! So, so weak!</font>

355
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:54,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Your inferior species is just so weak!</font>

356
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:03,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Let's escape with her
out the back door!</font>

357
00:21:03,990 --> 00:21:05,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But they might already be there!</font>

358
00:21:05,790 --> 00:21:06,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We'll be fine!</font>

359
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:07,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hold it!</font>

360
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:12,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Doctor!</font>

361
00:21:12,670 --> 00:21:13,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You mustn't go home!</font>

362
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:14,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Wha...?!</font>

363
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:16,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Move! We have to save Bell-mère!</font>

364
00:21:16,710 --> 00:21:18,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nojiko! Nami!</font>

365
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:20,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Listen closely, you two!</font>

366
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:21,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">This isn't the time to–</font>

367
00:21:21,890 --> 00:21:23,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Actually, this is the perfect time...</font>

368
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:26,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I have to tell you something horrible!</font>

369
00:21:28,270 --> 00:21:29,100
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Doctor?</font>

370
00:21:31,230 --> 00:21:33,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère!</font>

371
00:21:41,610 --> 00:21:45,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I can't do anything!
These guys are real monsters!</font>

372
00:21:45,780 --> 00:21:46,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm gonna die!</font>

373
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:49,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nojiko! Nami!</font>

374
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère!</font>

375
00:21:51,210 --> 00:21:53,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Don't throw your life
away over your pride!</font>

376
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:55,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Some fights aren't worth it!</font>

377
00:21:55,670 --> 00:21:58,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Some issues can be
solved with money!</font>

378
00:21:58,710 --> 00:22:00,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Mr. Gen...</font>

379
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:03,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That's right, Miss Marine.</font>

380
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:06,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's 100,000 per adult
and 50,000 per child.</font>

381
00:22:06,810 --> 00:22:10,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pay for your whole family if you want
to live. Be grateful I'm even telling you.</font>

382
00:22:10,810 --> 00:22:12,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">My whole family?</font>

383
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That's 200,000 in total.</font>

384
00:22:16,650 --> 00:22:18,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">How much do you have, all together?</font>

385
00:22:19,690 --> 00:22:21,700
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Including what I've squirreled away...</font>

386
00:22:21,700 --> 00:22:22,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">a little over 100,000...</font>

387
00:22:24,910 --> 00:22:28,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hey! There's a meal for
three people in here!</font>

388
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh?</font>

389
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:32,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">A family of three, huh?</font>

390
00:22:34,170 --> 00:22:36,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I almost forgot!</font>

391
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:42,170
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She invited my friend and me
to dinner tonight!</font>

392
00:22:42,170 --> 00:22:43,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Come on, Bell-mère.</font>

393
00:22:43,800 --> 00:22:45,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hurry and pay your amount.</font>

394
00:22:45,890 --> 00:22:48,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Our delicious dinner will get cold!</font>

395
00:22:48,350 --> 00:22:49,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Mr. Gen...</font>

396
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:51,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I hear you've got 100,000.</font>

397
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Thank goodness you have enough!</font>

398
00:22:53,980 --> 00:22:56,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Now everyone in the village can live!</font>

399
00:22:56,690 --> 00:22:57,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's true.</font>

400
00:22:57,940 --> 00:23:02,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">The village register has no record
of her getting married or giving birth.</font>

401
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:04,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She's single.</font>

