00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Do you understand?!</font>

407
00:23:09,870 --> 00:23:13,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">There's no proof that you two
and Bell-mère are family!</font>

408
00:23:13,370 --> 00:23:16,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Leave this island before
they take notice of you!</font>

409
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:17,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Escape across the sea!</font>

410
00:23:18,380 --> 00:23:20,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Then all three of you can survive!</font>

411
00:23:21,630 --> 00:23:25,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's reckless to send you two
out to sea at such a young age.</font>

412
00:23:25,130 --> 00:23:28,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">A lot could go wrong,
but at least you'll have–</font>

413
00:23:28,470 --> 00:23:29,100
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">No.</font>

414
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:32,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I don't want to.</font>

415
00:23:32,390 --> 00:23:36,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I... want to live in this village...</font>

416
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:37,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Is it because we're poor?</font>

417
00:23:38,150 --> 00:23:41,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Is that why we can't be
Bell-mère's kids anymore?!</font>

418
00:23:41,900 --> 00:23:44,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Why? Why?!</font>

419
00:23:47,950 --> 00:23:49,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Thank goodness.</font>

420
00:23:49,490 --> 00:23:51,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Then everything will be fine.</font>

421
00:23:51,740 --> 00:23:53,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Alright, we'll leave the village!</font>

422
00:23:52,660 --> 00:23:53,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82" color="#d6d6d6">Nojiko!</font>

423
00:23:53,830 --> 00:23:54,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Let's go!</font>

424
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:57,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">This way Bell-mère gets to live!</font>

425
00:24:12,930 --> 00:24:14,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hold it.</font>

426
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:16,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Who said I paid for myself?</font>

427
00:24:17,730 --> 00:24:20,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That 100,000 is
for my two daughters.</font>

428
00:24:20,860 --> 00:24:22,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Not for me.</font>

429
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:25,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère! What are you–</font>

430
00:24:25,740 --> 00:24:27,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm sorry, Mr. Gen.</font>

431
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:30,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I can't just say I don't have a family.</font>

432
00:24:30,320 --> 00:24:33,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Even if it costs me my life.</font>

433
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That fool...!</font>

434
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:39,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah, maybe we're not
related by blood...</font>

435
00:24:40,670 --> 00:24:42,170
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">but we're a family.</font>

436
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:45,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I want to be their mom,
even if it's only in name.</font>

437
00:24:46,670 --> 00:24:47,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">They're...</font>

438
00:24:48,430 --> 00:24:49,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">my girls.</font>

439
00:24:50,550 --> 00:24:53,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">– Bell-mère!
– Bell-mère!</font>

440
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:52,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82" color="#d6d6d6">Wait, you two!</font>

441
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:57,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>I wish someone richer
had adopted me instead!</i></font>

442
00:24:57,600 --> 00:24:59,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It was just a lie!</font>

443
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:01,100
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I was lying!</font>

444
00:25:01,100 --> 00:25:03,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">– Bell-mère!
– Bell-mère!</font>

445
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:18,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I wanted...</font>

446
00:25:18,620 --> 00:25:21,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">to buy you lots more
books and clothes...</font>

447
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:23,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'm sorry!</font>

448
00:25:23,630 --> 00:25:26,170
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I wish I could've been
a better mother!</font>

449
00:25:26,170 --> 00:25:27,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">That's not true!</font>

450
00:25:27,510 --> 00:25:29,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We don't need anything!
Just don't die!</font>

451
00:25:29,380 --> 00:25:30,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Stay with us forever!</font>

452
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:34,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I want you to see the map
of the world I'm gonna draw!</font>

453
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:37,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah... your map...</font>

454
00:25:38,520 --> 00:25:39,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Make your dream...</font>

455
00:25:40,270 --> 00:25:42,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">come true!</font>

456
00:25:44,110 --> 00:25:45,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Live!</font>

457
00:25:45,570 --> 00:25:47,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bell-mère!</font>

458
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:52,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">These are your girls, I take it?</font>

459
00:25:54,780 --> 00:25:56,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah, that's right!</font>

460
00:25:56,910 --> 00:25:59,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Promise me you won't
